 contracts|date=2017-01-12|accessdate=2017-01-12|publisher=Arsenal F.C.|language=en|archive-date=2017-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113153408/http://www.arsenal.com/news/news-archive/20170112/french-trio-sign-new-long-term-contracts|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2日後，在客勝史雲斯4比0的比賽中，他為球隊上陣第200場比賽<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/85/england/2017/01/14/31518072/koscielny-reaches-200-premier-league-appearances-for-arsenal|title=Koscielny reaches 200 Premier League appearances for Arsenal|date=2017-01-14|accessdate=2017-01-18|publisher=Goal.com|language=en|archive-date=2017-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118224339/http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/85/england/2017/01/14/31518072/koscielny-reaches-200-premier-league-appearances-for-arsenal|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/38539469|title=Swansea City 0–4 Arsenal|date=2017-01-14|accessdate=2017-01-18|publisher=BBC Sports|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111201816/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/38539469|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在聯賽煞科戰對陣愛華頓的比賽中，他在侵犯[[恩纳·瓦伦西亚|-{zh-hans:恩纳·瓦伦西亚;zh-hk:安拿·華倫西亞;zh-tw:恩納·瓦倫西亞;}-]]後被球證出示紅牌，停賽3場，缺席[[2017年英格兰足总杯决赛|2017年英格兰足总杯决赛]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Laurent Koscielny: Arsenal defender to miss FA Cup final after appeal fails|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/40020494|website=BBC Sport|date=2017-05-23|language=en|access-date=2017-06-08|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021090054/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/40020494|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

